        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段回吐 恒指跌149點報21316點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">外圍股市回吐，港股今早亦低開。恒生指數開市報21316點，跌148點或0.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報4908點，跌72點或1.46%；國企指數以7911點開市，跌71點或0.89%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240102_FI_HKSTOCK_SOURCE-BP.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240102_FI_HKSTOCK_SOURCE-BP.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股跌多於升，阿里巴巴(09988)開報107元，跌2.64%；騰訊(00700)開報450.6元，跌1.18%；美團(03690)開報143.1元，跌2.52%。滙控(00005)開報79.65元，升1.08%；友邦(01299)開報52.25元，跌0.85%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：赤峰黃金官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_Chifeng-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：赤峰黃金官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_Chifeng-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：赤峰黃金官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">現貨金價創新高，金礦股與金飾零售股普遍炒上。紫金礦業(02899)開報17.44元，升1.28%；招金(01818)開報18.5元，升3.35%；赤峰黃金(06693)開報27.5元，升6.8%。老鋪黃金(06181)開報853元，升3.27%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中集集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250416_FI_source-web_02039-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中集集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250416_FI_source-web_02039-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中集集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中集集團(02039)發盈喜，料首季多賺最多6.77倍；該股今早開報5.1元，漲7.6%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14858179-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c149%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b121316%e9%bb%9e",
